Â  This utility is still under development, my intentions are so that you can end skyrim process when the game freezes, I made this because i'm tired of
having to logoff whenever it happened.

[size=5]Using Skyrim_Ckiller:[/size]
[size=3]Just run Skyrim_Ckiller.exe before the game and press F7 key to kill it.(there is no need to use NMM)
Since it's currently under development you may have to alt+tab or press windows key to be able to use it.
(maybe it won't even work i'm posting it now to have some friends download it and help me (help is welcome));[/size]
